name: Facture du 1er nov a maintenant
query:
SELECT si.posting_date, si.Customer, sii.base_net_amount, st.sales_person, sii.sales_order, sii.parent
FROM `tabSales Invoice` si 
LEFT JOIN `tabSales Invoice Item` sii ON si.name=sii.parent
LEFT JOIN `tabSales Team` st ON st.parent=si.name 
WHERE  sii.sales_order is null and si.docstatus=1
ORDER BY st.sales_person

name: Suppliers with Invoices
query:
SELECT
  tabSupplier.supplier_name as "Supplier:Link/supplier:200",
  tabAddress.address_line1 as "Address Line 1:text:250",
  tabAddress.address_line2 as "Address Line 2:text:150",
  tabAddress.city as "City:text:150",
  tabAddress.pincode as "Postal Code:text:85",
  tabAddress.state as "Province:text:85",
  tabAddress.country as "Country:text:85"
FROM tabSupplier
  INNER JOIN `tabPurchase Invoice`
    ON `tabPurchase Invoice`.supplier = tabSupplier.name
  LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabDynamic Link`
    ON tabSupplier.name = `tabDynamic Link`.link_name
  INNER JOIN tabAddress
    ON `tabDynamic Link`.parent = tabAddress.name
WHERE `tabPurchase Invoice`.`posting_date` BETWEEN %(from_date)s AND %(to_date)s
GROUP BY tabSupplier.supplier_name

name: First Open Task by Open Project - ngoyette
query:
SELECT
  tabProject.name as "Project:Link/Project:250",
  tabProject.project_amount_from_so as "Amount:Currency:90",
  tabProject.sub_type as "SubType:text:105",
  tabTask.subject as "Subject:text:250",
  tabTask.name as "Task:Link/Task:100",
  tabTask.status as "Status:text:105",
  tabProject.expected_end_date as "Exp. End Date:date:90",
  tabProject.project_manager as "Project Manager:Link/User:150",
  tabProject.type as "Type:text:105",
  tabTask.assigned_to as "Assigned To:Link/User:150"
FROM tabProject, tabTask
WHERE tabTask.status <> 'Closed'
AND tabProject.name = tabTask.project
AND tabTask.status <> 'Cancelled'
AND tabProject.type = 'Graphic'
AND (tabProject.status = 'Open' OR tabProject.status = 'Project Without Orders')
AND
(
	SELECT tt.assigned_to
    	FROM tabTask tt
	WHERE tt.status <> 'Closed'
	AND tt.status <> 'Cancelled'
	AND tabProject.name = tt.project
	GROUP By tt.project
	ORDER BY tt.subject
	LIMIT 1
) IN ("ngoyette@shei.sh", "nlaperriere@shei.sh")
GROUP BY tabProject.name
ORDER BY tabTask.subject
report_name: First Open Task by Open Project - ngoyette

name: Contacts per Customer
query:
SELECT
  tabContact.name as "Name:Link/Contact:250",
  tabContact.first_name as "Fist Name:Data:250",
  tabContact.last_name as "Last Name:Data:250",
  tabContact.email_id as "Email:Data:250",
  tabContact.phone as "Phone:Data:90"
FROM `tabDynamic Link`
INNER JOIN tabContact
ON `tabDynamic Link`.parent = tabContact.name
WHERE
  `tabDynamic Link`.parenttype = "Contact"
  AND `tabDynamic Link`.link_doctype = "Customer"
  AND `tabDynamic Link`.link_name = (%(customer)s)

name: Graphic Production
query:
SELECT
  tabProject.name as "Project:Link/Project:250",
  tabProject.project_amount_from_so as "Amount:Currency:90",
  tabProject.sub_type as "SubType:text:105",
  tabTask.subject as "Subject:text:250",
  tabTask.name as "Task:Link/Task:100",
  tabTask.status as "Status:text:105",
  tabProject.expected_end_date as "Exp. End Date:date:90",
  tabProject.project_manager as "Project Manager:Link/User:150",
  tabProject.type as "Type:text:105",
  tabTask.assigned_to as "Assigned To:Link/User:150"
FROM tabProject, tabTask
WHERE tabTask.status <> 'Closed'
AND tabProject.name = tabTask.project
AND tabTask.status <> 'Cancelled'
AND tabProject.sub_type IN ('Alto', 'Folia')
AND (tabProject.status = 'Open' OR tabProject.status = 'Project Without Orders')
AND
(
	SELECT tt.subject
    	FROM tabTask tt
	WHERE tt.status <> 'Closed'
	AND tt.status <> 'Cancelled'
	AND tabProject.name = tt.project
	AND tt.assigned_to NOT IN ('emontreuil@shei.sh', 'mhaineault@shei.sh')
	GROUP By tt.project
	ORDER BY tt.subject
	LIMIT 1
) IN ("FOLIA-07-MATERIAL ORDERING",
      "FOLIA-08-ARBORITE ORDERING",
      "FOLIA-09-ARBORITE INSPECTION-CUT-CNC",
      "FOLIA-10-EDGES-INSERTS-MOUNTING-ETC",
      "FOLIA-11-GATHER HARDWARE-Z-CLIP-POST-ETC",
      "FOLIA-12-INSPECTION / PACKAGING",
      "FOLIA-13-ENTER FINISHED PRODUCTION IN ERP",
      "FOLIA-14-INVOICING",
      "FOLIA-15-SHIPPING",
      "ALTO-09-DEBURRING-CLEANING-PAINTING",
      "ALTO-10-SUBLIMATION ALTO OVEN",
      "ALTO-11-GATHER HARDWARE-Z-CLIP-POST-ETC",
      "ALTO-12-INSPECTION / PACKAGING",
      "ALTO-13-ENTER FINISHED PRODUCTION IN ERP",
      "ALTO-14-INVOICING",
      "ALTO-15-SHIPPING")
GROUP BY tabProject.name
ORDER BY tabTask.subject

name: Closed Task
query:
SELECT
  tabProject.name as "Project:Link/Project:250",
  tabProject.type as "Type:text:90",
  tabProject.sub_type as "SubType:text:90",
  tabProject.percent_complete as "Completion:text:50",
  tabTask.name as "Task:Link/Task:100",
  tabTask.subject as "Subject:text:250",
  tabTask.exp_end_date as "Exp End Date:date:90"
FROM tabProject, tabTask
WHERE tabProject.name = tabTask.project
AND tabTask.status = 'Closed'
AND tabTask.exp_end_date >= %(task_closed_from)s
AND tabTask.exp_end_date <= %(task_closed_to)s
ORDER BY tabProject.Name

name: Sommaire Journalier
query:
SELECT
    Distinct(`tabDelivery Note`.name) as "Delivery Note:Link/Delivery Note:100",
    tabProject.name as "Project:Link/Project:250",
    `tabDelivery Note`.transporter as "Transporter:text:90",
    `tabDelivery Note`.lr_no as "Waybill:text:90"
FROM 
    tabProject, 
    `tabDelivery Note`
WHERE 
    `tabDelivery Note`.project = tabProject.name
    AND `tabDelivery Note`.status != 'Completed'
    AND CURDATE() = `tabDelivery Note`.lr_date
ORDER BY tabProject.Name
